{"tid":107392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"口號同情趣app撞名     奶媽競選辦：設計師原創","createTime":"2017-02-04T12:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T06:03:53.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd7c3243f7a922032e9943c329e6c4d5b4aa521d","tid":107392,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170204/large/1486209809_300c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170204%2Flarge%2F1486209809_300c.jpg&h=d0ce3486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首參選人林鄭月娥昨日與競選辦成員出席造勢大會，以「We Connect 同行」作為競選口號，眾人均穿上印有We Connect的T恤，但有網民發現，該口號竟與一款情趣app的名字巧合地一樣，周六林鄭競選辦回覆傳媒查詢，指競選口號和標誌為劉小康和一批年青設計師原創。<br />\n<br />\n競選辦又稱，「同行 WeConnect」反映香港中西薈萃的獨特多元文化，用意是團結社會，與廣大市民同行，推動香港向前發展。<br />\n被網民意外發掘的情趣app可供iPhone與Android下載，在Google Play Store下載人次超過10萬，該款情趣app以手機操控震動器，讓夫妻遙距享受魚水之歡。"},{"pid":"0093e12b2b81637d9e2e10af2d251cee23851631","tid":107392,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"144575ca4e0f07043f68208119f1dae27c3103b9","tid":107392,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c3b6f3a8649bf432d5250c41daf3895e5e7a95","tid":107392,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:23:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3db79224e61215c1217cb074818535ef40aa0ae7","tid":107392,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0989cdadc8daef406b94d49a619108b65e1480b9","tid":107392,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit